title: Green Bean Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house with some vegan food offerings. Has a portobello mushroom panini, peanut butter and banana panini, soups, salads, rice and bean wrap, fair trade drinks. Soy milk is available. Offers a customer loyalty card. Wi-fi access with purchase. Open mic night every Thursdays.
